name: v3.25.0
body:
>[!IMPORTANT]
> `dd-trace-rb` (`datadog` gem) version is [v2.12](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-rb/releases/tag/v2.12.1)

```yml
# AWS Commercial
arn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2:25
arn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2-ARM:25
arn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3:25
arn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3-ARM:25

# AWS GovCloud
arn:aws:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2:25
arn:aws:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-2-ARM:25
arn:aws:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3:25
arn:aws:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Ruby3-3-ARM:25
```

## What's Changed
* chore(releases): add `mx-central-1` and `ap-southeast-7` regions by @duncanista in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/105
* chore: remove solargraph dependency. by @purple4reina in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/108
* chore: upgrade tracer to v2.12 by @duncanista in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/113

## New Contributors
* @apiarian-datadog made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/109
* @xopham made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/106
* @dependabot made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/112
* @purple4reina made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-rb/pull/108
